            fontSize: 13,
          ),
        ),
        trailing: Switch(
          value: value,
          onChanged: (v) {
            Future.delayed(
              const Duration(milliseconds: 350),
              () => onChanged(v),
            );
          },
          activeThumbColor: Theme.of(context).colorScheme.primary,
        ),
      ),
    );
